\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"最多叫守得精彩，唔會話自摸得靚。因為打邊隻係你決定，摸邊隻唔到你話事。"},{"pid":"336396d204807821c7a8d0d2837245693614d194","tid":2367460,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"跑馬仔靠運多"},{"pid":"5dbb2da0405a4a5eb6de312c3e26c943b7db8b1a","tid":2367460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"盲拳打死老師傅<br />\nbtw 每個人對「有技術」嘅定義都唔同<br />\n係你眼中嘅「有技術」可能係我眼中只係屎片一條"},{"pid":"48c8350e30a96a957e07f1d1d40ced8c9ca4c936","tid":2367460,"uid":201169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"336396d204807821c7a8d0d2837245693614d194","tid":2367460,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"跑馬仔靠運多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"我地打港式台牌，但我覺得適用於各類型既麻雀！"},{"pid":"6e7a58e1db7a5f92c14e11dcd57a148bf9e589fd","tid":2367460,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"why not both ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9cd7b957d1b9852280e50c7d3a82fa8e0d4821","tid":2367460,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317d90ac028a1921d19a2de961bf41b152d49688","tid":2367460,"uid":201169,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0c3372bc2c25547b12d1faac81598311493dd721","tid":2367460,"uid":43261,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"同打poker一樣<br />\n有技術EQ好<br />\n長玩會係正EV<br />\n大前題係要夠bankroll<br />\nsupport到你短期極黑仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"我都有玩poker，但我認為poker技術含量高好多。你每次call都有技術，甚至乎你可以揀唔去。<br />\n同麻雀唔同，你棄糊都要摸牌，所以我覺得唔可以用poker做比較。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"poker玩到最後blind愈嚟愈大<br />\n其實最後玩poker運氣佔好撚重"},{"pid":"eed6b8bbf7257ac7d6674140f2c920de7a52f2f8","tid":2367460,"uid":201169,"like